An <b>integral_shield</b> is a  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.component_shape_aspect"/> that implements the ARM concept
of  <express_ref linkend="Shield:arm:Shield_arm.Shield"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
