++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shield_mim.integral_shield.wr:WR1">
The <b>integral_shield</b> shall be related to at least one  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.component_definition"/> or to
at least one  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.component_shape_aspect"/> as the 'shielded item'.
